  <p><anchor n="T.50.2062.0901c25"/><lb ed="T" n="0901c25"/><persName key="A007862">釋淨真</persName>未詳姓氏。從<placeName key="PL000000008469">松江興聖寺</placeName><persName key="A007864">若平法<lb ed="T" n="0901c26"/>師</persName>薙染習賢首宗。<date from-iso="1239-02-13" key="j21736392173992" to-iso="1240-02-01">嘉熙三年</date>遊<placeName key="PL000000011305">浙江</placeName>諸剎。<lb ed="T" n="0901c27"/>因<placeName key="PL000000008367">錢塘江</placeName>壩毀。江濤泛溢災民。師以偈呈<lb ed="T" n="0901c28"/>安撫使<persName key="A007868">趙端明</persName>曰。海沸江河水接連。民居<lb ed="T" n="0901c29"/>蕩益憂煎。投身直入龍宮去。要止驚濤浪<lb ed="T" n="0902a01"/>拍天。遂投身於海。三日而返。謂居民曰。<persName key="A007862">我</persName><lb ed="T" n="0902a02"/>在龍宮說法龍神聽受。此<placeName key="PL000000008367">塘</placeName>不復毀矣。語<lb ed="T" n="0902a03"/>訖復投於海。<persName key="A007868">趙端明</persName>感其德具聞於朝。勅<lb ed="T" n="0902a04"/>賜<persName key="A007862">護國淨真法師</persName>。立祠於<placeName key="PL000000011515">杭</placeName>之會祠。</p>
